Title: Cheng Bo!
Description:
Cheng Bo is the Warbringer of Fire Camp Gai-Cho. While you've made a dent in their operations, you now have an opportunity to strike a major blow. 

Slay the Warbringer!
ObjectivesText: Kill Cheng-Bo at Fire Camp Gai-Cho in Townlong Steppes.
PortraitGiverText: The Warbringer of the Gai-Cho yaungol.
